Description: Co-designed with one of the world's most renowned jazz guitarists, the signature Kurt Rosenwinkel Premier SS features a spruce top for brightness and a center-block for maximum sustain. With minimal appointments, the Kurt Rosenwinkel SS is built for rich tone and high performance, featuring a comfortable C-shape neck profile and stopbar tailpiece. Its Honey Burst finish is complemented by a rosewood fretboard and chrome hardware.
